release_note: Fixes a crash that affected iPad users
New Copy anything as an image New Choose images from files Improved handwriting experience Bug fixes

Buckle up for Instaboard 2.0! We have so many exciting features for you: Instaboard PRO is here! Upgrade to get infinite permanent whiteboards and larger board space! Sign up to get 3 free boosters per month. A booster can make a board permanent removes the 24 hour expiration time Infinite canvas. You may choose to create a board with an infinite canvas size. Sticky note organizers: a new magical tool to organize your ideas! Templates: drag in a prebuilt template to speed up your workflow! More templates coming soon. And tons of enhancements and bug fixes.
Things will now automatically snap to places : You can now create and open boards even if you re offline.
Voice calling Sticky note textbox editing improvements
You can now drag PDF files onto Instaboard s home page. Last locations in boards are remembered. The straight line tool user experience is improved. Bug fixes
